---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import NewsletterForm from '../components/NewsletterForm.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Community — Zro2One"
  description="Join the Zro2One community. Three learning tracks — Foundation, Advanced, and Business — designed to meet you where you are and take you further."
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 sm:py-24">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black text-zro-dark mb-6">
        Learn together. Build together.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-zro-gray max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        AI moves fast. You don't have to figure it out alone. Join a community of people
        learning, building, and launching — at every level.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Three Tracks -->
    <div class="grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 mb-20">
      <!-- Track 1: Foundation -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 p-8 flex flex-col hover:border-emerald-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
        <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🟢</div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-zro-dark mb-2">Foundation</h2>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-emerald-600 mb-4">For curious professionals</p>
        <p class="text-zro-gray text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-1">
          You've heard about AI tools but haven't used them yet — or tried once and bounced off.
          This track gives you a structured on-ramp: what AI actually is, which tools matter for
          your work, and how to start using them with confidence. No coding required.
        </p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-zro-gray space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-emerald-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>Guided learning paths through Zro2One content</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-emerald-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>Weekly live sessions with walkthroughs</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-emerald-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>Ask questions in a judgment-free space</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-emerald-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>Cohort-based — learn alongside peers</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-xs text-zro-gray italic">
          Best for: mid-career and senior professionals, career changers, managers, educators
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Track 2: Advanced -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 p-8 flex flex-col hover:border-purple-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
        <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🟣</div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-zro-dark mb-2">Advanced</h2>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-purple-600 mb-4">For builders and practitioners</p>
        <p class="text-zro-gray text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-1">
          You already use AI tools and maybe build with them. You want to stay sharp, learn what's
          new, and swap notes with people at your level. This track is peer-driven — show and tell,
          not lecture and listen.
        </p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-zro-gray space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-purple-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>Biweekly show-and-tell sessions</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-purple-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>Share projects, tools, and workflows</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-purple-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>Deep-dives on new models, frameworks, and techniques</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-purple-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>Collaborative projects and challenges</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-xs text-zro-gray italic">
          Best for: developers, engineers, data scientists, AI-native professionals
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Track 3: Business -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 p-8 flex flex-col hover:border-amber-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
        <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🟠</div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-zro-dark mb-2">Business</h2>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-amber-600 mb-4">For aspiring founders</p>
        <p class="text-zro-gray text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-1">
          You can build things with AI — but turning skills into a business is a different game.
          This track covers idea validation, finding customers, pricing, MVP strategy, and the
          unglamorous work of going from side project to real revenue.
        </p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-zro-gray space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-amber-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>Idea validation frameworks</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-amber-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>Office hours with founders and mentors</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-amber-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>From MVP to first customer playbooks</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-amber-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>Accountability groups and peer feedback</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-xs text-zro-gray italic">
          Best for: technical people exploring entrepreneurship, freelancers, indie hackers
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- How It Works -->
    <div class="mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-black text-zro-dark mb-8 text-center">
        How it works
      </h2>
      <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl font-black text-emerald-500 mb-3">1</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-zro-dark mb-2">Pick your track</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-zro-gray">
            Choose the track that matches where you are right now. Not sure? Start with Foundation.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl font-black text-emerald-500 mb-3">2</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-zro-dark mb-2">Join the community</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-zro-gray">
            Get access to your track's channel, resources, and sessions. Everything is free.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl font-black text-emerald-500 mb-3">3</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-zro-dark mb-2">Show up and grow</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-zro-gray">
            Attend sessions, ask questions, share what you learn. The community gets better when you participate.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <div class="mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-black text-zro-dark mb-8 text-center">
        Questions
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-zro-dark mb-1">Is this really free?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-zro-gray">
            Yes. The community, the content, and the sessions are all free. We believe AI education
            should be accessible to everyone.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-zro-dark mb-1">Can I switch tracks?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-zro-gray">
            Absolutely. Tracks aren't gates — they're starting points. Join multiple if you want.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-zro-dark mb-1">What's the time commitment?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-zro-gray">
            Foundation runs weekly sessions (~1 hour). Advanced and Business run biweekly. Everything
            is recorded if you can't make it live.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-zro-dark mb-1">Do I need to know how to code?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-zro-gray">
            Not for Foundation or Business. The Advanced track assumes some technical background, but
            there's no strict requirement.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="text-center rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 border border-gray-200 p-10 sm:p-14 mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-black text-zro-dark mb-4">
        Ready to join?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-zro-gray mb-8 max-w-lg mx-auto">
        Sign up below and we'll get you into the right track. First cohort launching soon.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://forms.gle/PLACEHOLDER"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-block bg-zro-dark text-white font-bold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors text-sm"
      >
        Join the Community →
      </a>
      <p class="text-xs text-zro-gray mt-4">Free forever. No spam. Just learning.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Newsletter -->
    <div>
      <NewsletterForm />
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
